            <h1>Crime and abuse</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/kriminalitet_og_overgrep_150x113.jpg" alt="Harassing man" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">The fight against crime will be fought on a broad front. Combating international and organised crime will be given priority. The Government wishes to strengthen preventive efforts in the widest possible sense. The victims of serious crimes, and crimes of violence in particular, shall be ensured better follow-up.</p>
            <img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/kriminalitet_og_overgrep_150x113.jpg" alt="Harassing man" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p>The main goal of the <em>Ministry of Justice and the Police</em> is to ensure that fundamental guarantees of due process protection are maintained and developed. It is an overriding goal to ensure the security of society and the individual.</p>
<p><br />On this page you will find general information and documents relating to crime and abuse. You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.<br /></p></div>
